{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9b8fe06914","title":"为中央社会部题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ea89de49ae","index":0,"year":1937,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"9b8fe06914"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji11","name":"毛泽东全集第11卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji11.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji11":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c24d110a0","type":"paragraph","text":"为中央社会部题词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"9b8fe06914"},{"id":"ccf6124341","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年）为竞即是为人民服务","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"9b8fe06914"},{"id":"bd3672dd56","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东[中央社会部是公安部的前身，最早是1931年11月成立的中华苏维埃政治保卫局：1935年11月随红军长征到达陕北，更名组建成了西北政治保卫局，成为保卫中共中央的主要机构，由毛泽东的老部下周兴任局长。1937年又改名为边区保安处，它是陕甘宁边区公开的治安管理部门，仍由周和情报部的工作人员基本上也是从边区保安处调出，所以保安处与社会部原本是一个机构的添生关系。鉴于边保谢好素特工作的重要性，毛泽东在中央社会部内部刊物上，做了“为党即是为人民服务”的题词。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"9b8fe06914"},{"id":"b12978cbf7","type":"paragraph","text":"龙人题馆万克中足庆毛泽东为中央社会部的题词","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"9b8fe06914"}],"page":{"id":"4b4773d4d3","publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"9b8fe06914","start":434,"end":435}}}},"__N_SSG":true}